name: East-1
content: East-1 was the callsign of a human individual who served in the Preox-Morlana Corporate Tactical Forces. During the Imperial Era, East-1 participated in an ambush on Ferrix against Cassian Jeron Andor. East-1 tried to snipe Cassian Andor and Luthen Rael, but lost them in the city. He later rescued Deputy Inspector Syril Karn after being detained by Andor and helped to recover the North Team after Luthen Rael had exploded a landspeeder.
